description:
Turkish basketball player Enes Kanter Freedom becomes a US citizen and patriotically changes his name. Enes Kanter Freedom to Americans who criticize America: "Please, keep your mouth shut and stop criticizing the greatest nation in the world." Are professional athletes starting to be red pilled? CNN host Chris Cuomo used his media sources to find out info on brother's, disgraced New York Governor Andrew Cuomo’s, accusers. Biden White House is thinking of putting Kamala Harris on the Supreme Court. Will Biden run in 2024? Drive-By Media helped hide the real Joe Biden by censoring Hunter Biden stories. Caller celebrates Enes Kanter Freedom gaining his citizenship the legal way.
